The Hunchback of Notre Dame;;70;;71;;G;;An animated Disney adventure follows disfigured Quasimodo (Tom Hulce), the bell-ringer of Notre Dame Cathedral, who bides his time locked away in a tower. With only gargoyles to keep him company, Quasimodo longs to be with other people, leading to his chance encounter with the enchanting Gypsy Esmeralda (Demi Moore). When the beautiful young woman catches the attention of Quasimodo's guardian, sinister Frollo (Tony Jay), Quasimodo must help to keep her out of his clutches.;;Drama,Animation,Kids & family;;Gary Trousdale,Kirk Wise;;1996;;Tom Hulce,Demi Moore,Tony Jay,Kevin Kline,Paul Kandel,Jason Alexander,Charles Kimbrough,Mary Wickes,David Ogden Stiers,Heidi Mollenhauer,Mary Kay Bergman,Corey Burton,Jim Cummings,Bill Fagerbakke,Dana Hill,Patrick Pinney,Gary Trousdale,Frank Welker,Jane Withers;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1073037-hunchback_of_notre_dame